  Before shipping for real:
    1. Generate EdDSA keys once: Sparkle bin/generate_keys
    2. Put the PUBLIC key in Info.plist as SUPublicEDKey (never commit the private key)
    3. After each release zip is built, sign it:
         sign_update dist/MacWispr-X.Y.Z-macos-arm64.zip
    4. Fill sparkle:edSignature and length below with sign_update output
    5. Deploy this file to fuckwisprflow.com

  See docs/SPARKLE.md for the full release flow.
-->
